title: Better Man (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
Who else heard this song for the first time ever during the Red TV release and fell in love with it? This heart-breaking ballad was written a while ago and given to another band, and they had a lot of success with the song!
Find out all about it as we deep dive (and deep cry) into Better Man!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
